00374 Long64_t MakeClassSkeleton::LoadTree(Long64_t entry)
00375 {
00376 // Set the environment to read one entry
00377    if (!fChain) return -5;
00378    Long64_t centry = fChain->LoadTree(entry);
00379    if (centry < 0) return centry;
00380    if (!fChain->InheritsFrom(TChain::Class()))  return centry;
00381    TChain *chain = (TChain*)fChain;
00382    if (chain->GetTreeNumber() != fCurrent) {
00383       fCurrent = chain->GetTreeNumber();
00384       Notify();
00385    }
00386    return centry;
00387 }
